# Yamang coding conventions

Before editing application code, follow **docs/process/CODING_CONVENTIONS.md** (layer imports, lint pipeline, CC-05 comments, naming sampling).

- Domain/shared **must not** import `@app/*` (ESLint enforced).
- Run **`npm run lint`** before claiming work complete; hooks exhaustive-deps are errors.
